  '''
                                                                                  
   Usage: dev-space [OPTIONS] COMMAND [ARGS]...                                   
                                                                                  
   Agent-first development environment orchestrator.                              
                                                                                  
  ╭─ Options ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────╮
  │ --quiet               -q            Suppress stderr logs.                    │
  │ --verbose             -v            Full debug trace to stderr.              │
  │ --format                      TEXT  Structured output format                 │
  │                                     (json|jsonl|md).                         │
  │                                     [default: jsonl]                         │
  │ --rich                              Force human-friendly Rich output.        │
  │ --lane                        TEXT  Identity lane (human or agent).          │
  │                                     [default: agent]                         │
  │ --install-completion                Install completion for the current       │
  │                                     shell.                                   │
  │ --show-completion                   Show completion for the current shell,   │
  │                                     to copy it or customize the              │
  │                                     installation.                            │
  │ --help                              Show this message and exit.              │
  ╰──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────╯
  ╭─ Commands ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────╮
  │ bootstrap   Bootstraps the isolated dev-space environment.                   │
  │ shell-init  Outputs a sourceable shell profile.                              │
  │             Usage: eval "$(dev-space shell-init bash)"                       │
  │ qa          Zero-Trust QA Pipeline Plugin (ADR-008).                         │
  │ gh          GitHub Subcommands (ADR-002)                                     │
  │ session     Issue-scoped worker sessions and verified PR handoff             │
  │ worktree    Git Worktree Subcommands                                         │
  │ daemon      Daemon Lifecycle Management (ADR-006)                            │
  │ logs        Log Search (ADR-006)                                             │
  │ project     GitHub Project v2 control-plane reconciliation                   │
  │ issue       Planner-owned issue specifications and lifecycle transitions     │
  ╰──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────╯
  
  
